 gather to hear 4\, yes 4\, dynamic presentations\, all of which pertain to
  the subject of **Sustained Engagement.** You'll learn how to not be overw
 helmed by the sheer amount of depressing news broadcasts\, how to read bet
 ween the lines of what these newscasts are telling you\, and how to engage
  in a thoughtful manner. Speakers will include: 1. JimC- publisher of the 
 [Politics Is Emotional Substack](politicsisemotional.substack.com) 2. Leo
LOCATION:Allen County Public Library - Main\, 900 Library Plz\, Meeting Ro
 om A\, Fort Wayne\, IN\, 46802
URL:https://www.mobilize.us/indivisiblenortheastindiana/event/955589/
X-SOURCE:Indivisible Central Indiana (Mobilize)
END:VEVENT
